{"type":null,"faqId":49705,"title":"声控拍照是否可以自定义拍照词","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body1395731\"><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264287__p52595892\">不可以。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264287__p3600986\">请使用“相机”的声控拍照设置界面中提示的拍照词拍摄。默认声控拍照词为“拍照”、“茄子”、“Cheese\"，手机周边音量达到一定大小时也将自动拍照。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264287__p32408880\">设置超级夜景拍照参数</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264287__p23244472\">进入“相机”，点击<span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79d40_i3xns.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span>&gt; “超级夜景”，然后点击“自动”，可以选择ISO和曝光参数。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264287__p7873657\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79d41_rxvzn.jpg\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79d42_rslwv.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264287__p3754054\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79d43_hrulr.jpg\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79d44_6yvok.jpg\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264287__p33786486\"></p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022264287","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448590015000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publi